{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"51278-sahana-makes-music","title":"Sahana Makes Music","description":"Sahana’s home is too quiet. How can Sahana liven it up? She starts creating some music of her own. Listen in.","language":"English","langCode":"en","isRtl":false,"level":"2","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Ravi  Mundoli"],"illustrators":["Noorain   Ahmed"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Pratham Books","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/51278-sahana-makes-music"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/725481/size3/36bebfc2c6bd04e5fa90fc5082458ae6.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/725481/size6/36bebfc2c6bd04e5fa90fc5082458ae6.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/90574/size6/d0c171f8fd51417f9b185a6b68986e37.jpg","text":"Sahana is trying to read.\nWhy is the park so noisy?","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/90892/size6/bd59f16e0f2cbe5112db6c88fb30a0e8.jpg","text":"DRRRRRRRRR\nTHUD\nDhum Dhum\nRATATATATT","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/90576/size6/68d9dfbc5616923a685f631cc9b0bc4c.jpg","text":"Sahana is bored.\nWhy is her home\nso silent?","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/90577/size6/dfc39db9f09a38d2c84c81c5398fabae.jpg","text":"THUMP\nTOK\nTOK\nTOK\nSahana likes sounds.\nShe likes music.\nShe starts hitting\neverything with her fists.\nTHUMP","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/90578/size6/bac7477c40529e482ff251b6057f2f46.jpg","text":"CLANG\nCHIIINNNGGG\nBANG","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/90894/size6/772f21a1b7245cd2cb4265c3f7261dd7.jpg","text":"OWW\nPLOONG\nTANG\nPLING\nShe hits her hand\nwith the spoon.\nTING","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/90607/size6/7f802a04db777e28b2ade143c34e1d10.jpg","text":"Sahana taps on the glasses one by one.\nSo many sounds.\nPING\nTING\nPING\nTING","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/90608/size6/cfc6b5852ffc3d38c572e31cc1ce912a.jpg","text":"TING\nSahana taps lightly.","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/90609/size6/d6a884429709236beee6f854565c8ab4.jpg","text":"TOOONNNNNNGGGG\nSahana strikes\nthe glasses hard.","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/90610/size6/903f77b30ba5720509662750d8de5ed5.jpg","text":"Sahana slides her spoon all the \nway across the row of glasses.\nShe taps on the glass with lots of water.\nIt goes pht pht pht pht.\nShe taps on the glass with not much water.\nIt goes krrrinn krinnn krinnn krinnnnnng!","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/90611/size6/72edf8405963d9e6c6cb9cc760a79045.jpg","text":"“I am making music!”\nsays Sahana.","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/90612/size6/aae953d4436590ba8e32057a196c5759.jpg","text":"Sounds are invisible waves in the air that reach your ears. \nThe bigger or louder the sound, the higher the wave. \nThe smaller the sound, the lower the wave.\nLOW\nHIGH","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":12,"words":162}}